'''金點新秀設計獎'''（[[英語|英語]]譯名：'''{{lang|en|Young Pin Design Award}}'''），是臺灣[[新一代設計展|新一代設計展]]的競賽獎項。

== 歷史沿革 ==
「新一代設計展」為全球規模最大的設計人才與創意展覽的交流平台，由經濟部及教育部共同指導，經濟部工業局主辦、台灣設計研究院執行，是台灣設計界學子展現學習成果的重要舞台，也是企業發掘優秀設計人才、促進產學交流的平台，於2015年改為「金點新秀設計獎」<ref>{{cite news | title = 金點概念設計獎徵件 總獎金100萬元 | publisher = 自由時報 | url = http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/1332629 | date = 2015-05-29 | author = 吳柏軒 | accessdate = 2016-05-22 | language = zh-hant | archive-date = 2016-06-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160624114413/http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/1332629 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = 39年來首次 2020新一代設計展改採線上展覽 | publisher = 經濟日報 | url = https://money.udn.com/money/story/11799/4402496 | date = 2020-03-10 | author = 陳華焜 | language = zh-hant | accessdate = 2020-08-27 | archive-date = 2020-03-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200312012544/https://money.udn.com/money/story/11799/4402496 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2018年主辦單位新增「創業潛力特別獎」，該獎項協助獲獎作品與合適之廠商洽談後續合作及開發的可能性<ref>{{cite news | title = 新一代設計展今年大改革！ 學生免場租、獨立企業導覽 | publisher = 東森新聞 | url = https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180223/1118242.htm | date = 2018-02-23 | author = 盧映慈 | accessdate = 2019-05-14 | language = zh-hant | archive-date = 2019-05-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190514082438/https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180223/1118242.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = 參展費用高？新一代設計展推革新！同學免交場租 | publisher = 中國時報 | url = https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180223004723-260405 | date = 2018-02-23 | author = 林宜靜 | accessdate = 2019-05-14 | language = zh-hant | archive-date = 2019-05-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190514082437/https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180223004723-260405 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2019年再新增「社會設計類」，該獎項著重於設計者對社會議題或制度提出的設計理念<ref>{{cite news | title = 金點新秀設計獎倒數3天 今年新增兩獎項 | publisher = 中國時報 | url = https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20190304003216-260405 | date = 2019-03-04 | author = 李欣恬 | accessdate = 2019-05-14 | language = zh-hant | archive-date = 2019-05-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190514082436/https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20190304003216-260405 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

