== 爭議問題 ==
2016年包裝設計類金點新秀年度最佳設計獎得主「專業工具」{{NoteTag|1=「專業工具」指導老師許得輝，設計團隊：史允中、謝孟祺、 葉昱賢、曾昱嘉、張允嘉、吳晉瑋、吳兆晉。}}，是來自[[新北市私立復興高級商工職業學校|新北市私立復興高級商工職業學校]]的設計作品，事後傳出涉嫌抄襲國外的包裝設計<ref>{{cite news | title = 金點新秀獎得主復興商工學生　被控抄襲西班牙學生作品 | publisher = 東森新聞 | url = http://fashion.ettoday.net/news/701184 | date = 2016-05-19 | author =  | accessdate = 2016-05-21 | language = zh-hant | archive-date = 2016-05-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160520151333/http://fashion.ettoday.net/news/701184 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = 金點新秀設計獎 復興商工爆抄襲 | publisher = 中國時報 | url = http://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20160520000638-260107 | date = 2016-05-20 | author = 廖智怡 | accessdate = 2016-05-21 | language = zh-hant | archive-date = 2016-05-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160520144311/http://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20160520000638-260107 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。經主辦單位於同年5月21日召開作品覆核審定會議後，裁決取消得獎資格，該屆以「從缺」辦理<ref>{{cite news | title = 復興商工爆抄襲獲獎　金點新秀獎決議撤銷得獎資格 | publisher = 東森新聞 | url = http://fashion.ettoday.net/news/702640 | date = 2016-05-21 | author = 蔡惠如 | accessdate = 2016-05-21 | language = zh-hant | archive-date = 2016-05-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160522121145/http://fashion.ettoday.net/news/702640 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = 和國外作品「相似度高」　金點新秀設計首獎遭撤銷 | publisher = 蘋果日報蘋果即時 | url = http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20160522/867567/ | date = 2016-05-22 | author = 許敏溶 | accessdate = 2016-05-22 | language = zh-hant | archive-date = 2016-06-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160609174509/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20160522/867567/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。該事件是設計獎首次有首獎作品遭檢舉撤銷獎項<ref>{{cite news | title = 設計展爆抄襲 首獎遭撤 | publisher = 蘋果日報 | url = http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/headline/20160522/37228430/ | date = 2016-05-22 | author = 許敏溶 | accessdate = 2016-05-23 | language = zh-hant | archive-date = 2016-05-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160521220312/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/headline/20160522/37228430/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

